title: [inSurance Claim] - Follow up #Qmb4AnM
body:
Wallet 0x9d7a81addb2313dca15833536345bd6d2ee9cc82 has bought and sold Iron token withing 6 min difference (based on the timestamps). No losses were incurred. 

Information can be verified here:
https://polygonscan.com/token/0xd86b5923f3ad7b585ed81b448170ae026c65ae9a?a=0x9d7a81addb2313dca15833536345bd6d2ee9cc82

TITAN tokens have no trace in the wallet of the policyholder:
https://polygonscan.com/token/0xaaa5b9e6c589642f98a1cda99b9d024b8407285a?a=0x9d7a81addb2313dca15833536345bd6d2ee9cc82

[Resolution]:
Declined. 
Reasons:
1. IRON token was bought and sold without losses
2. TITAN token hasn't gone through the wallet.

[Message for the policy holder]:
Please contact t.me/insureteam if you think some details were missed by the support team.
